# TIME BEYOND US - Development Status

## Latest Update: Backtesting System Complete (v66.0.0)

### BACKTESTING SYSTEM - PRODUCTION READY

The comprehensive backtesting system has been completed with all features:

#### Enhanced Backtesting Engine (`backtest_engine.ts`)
- Multi-asset support (stocks, crypto, forex, commodities)
- Multi-timeframe analysis with signal aggregation
- Enhanced slippage models (fixed, volume-based, volatility-based)
- Enhanced commission models (percent, fixed, tiered)
- Position sizing methods (fixed, Kelly, volatility targeting, risk parity)
- Walk-forward optimization
- Monte Carlo simulation
- Comprehensive risk metrics (Ulcer Index, Pain Ratio, Recovery Factor, Tail Ratio)

#### Data Caching System (`data_cache.ts`)
- LRU cache for fast in-memory access
- File-based persistence for larger datasets
- Automatic data expiration
- Data quality checking (missing data detection, outlier detection)
- Forward-fill for missing candles

#### Strategy Optimization
- Grid search optimization with Pareto frontier
- Genetic algorithm optimization
- Parameter sensitivity analysis
- Multi-objective optimization (Sharpe, return, drawdown, win rate)

#### Multi-Asset Portfolio Backtesting
- Portfolio-level backtesting across multiple assets
- Correlation matrix analysis
- Portfolio optimization (Markowitz mean-variance)
- Rebalancing strategies (daily, weekly, monthly, quarterly)
- Risk allocation analysis
- Sector/asset class diversification metrics

#### Historical Data Integration
- Multiple providers (Finnhub, TwelveData, Coinbase)
- Automatic provider fallback
- Data alignment across assets
- Missing data handling

#### Results Visualization
- Equity curve charts
- Drawdown curve charts
- Monthly returns heatmap
- Trade distribution (by day, hour, duration)
- Trade scatter plots

#### API Endpoints
- POST /api/backtest/run - Run basic backtest
- POST /api/backtest/enhanced - Run enhanced backtest with full metrics
- POST /api/backtest/optimize - Run parameter optimization
- GET /api/backtest/results/:id - Get stored result
- GET /api/backtest/results - List all results
- DELETE /api/backtest/results/:id - Delete result
- GET /api/backtest/visualization/:id - Get chart-ready data
- POST /api/backtest/walk-forward - Walk-forward analysis
- POST /api/backtest/monte-carlo - Monte Carlo simulation
- POST /api/backtest/multi-asset - Portfolio backtest
- POST /api/backtest/portfolio-optimization - Optimize weights
- POST /api/backtest/correlation-analysis - Correlation matrix

### Files Modified/Created
